<P>FREE THOUGHTS UPON FAITH: OR THE RELIGION OF NATURE.</P>
<P>A POEM, WITH NOTES.</P>
<P><FIGURE>
</FIGURE></P>
<P>PRINTED IN THE YEAR, M.DCC.LVIII.</P>
